    <refsection id="Description_PotentialSensor">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            This block is used to measure the voltage with respect to the
            reference voltage (<emphasis role="bold">Ground</emphasis> block) in an electrical circuit. The
            voltage is given to the explicit part of the model via an explicit
            output port.

        </para>
    </refsection>
